text: Elsa Guðrún Jónsdóttir (born 29 March 1986) is an Icelandic cross-country skier. She competed in the women's 10 kilometre freestyle at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Icelandic female cross-country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Iceland Category:Cross-country skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
